DESCRIPTION:
UK Shared Business Services Ltd acting on behalf of the contracting authority the Advisory, Conciliation and Arbitration Service (ACAS) have put in place a contract to appoint a supplier who will supply a solution to meet the below objectives:

(a) workforce management;

(b) automated call distribution;

(c) reporting;

(d) test and transition;

(e) compatibility;

(f) service level management.

This contract has been awarded following a further competition against CCS RM1045 network services framework Lot 5. The contract is for an initial 3 year period and has the option to extend for a further 2 years on an annual basis. The value of the initial 3 year period is 1 200 000,00 GBP ex VAT. The value for the optional extension shall not exceed 400 000,00 GBP ex VAT per annum.
